statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_reports;
SELECT report_id, source_url FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_age > 30;
SELECT user_id, user_gender FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_id = 101;
SELECT source_url, user_gender FROM website_traffic_reports ORDER BY user_age DESC;
SELECT report_id, user_age FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_age < 25 AND user_gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_age > 30 ORDER BY user_gender DESC, user_id ASC
SELECT user_id, user_age, user_gender FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_gender = 'Female' AND user_age < 25 ORDER BY user_id DESC
SELECT source_url, COUNT(*) AS traffic_count FROM website_traffic_reports GROUP BY source_url HAVING traffic_count > 5 ORDER BY traffic_count DESC
SELECT source_url FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_id IN (1, 2, 3) AND user_gender = 'Male' ORDER BY source_url ASC
SELECT user_id, user_age, user_gender FROM website_traffic_reports WHERE user_age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 AND user_gender IN ('Male', 'Female') ORDER BY user_age ASC
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_sources;
SELECT source_name, traffic_count FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count > 1000;
SELECT * FROM user_demographics ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, gender FROM user_demographics WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT MAX(traffic_count) AS max_traffic_count FROM website_traffic_sources;
SELECT source_name, traffic_count FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count > 100 ORDER BY traffic_count DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, location FROM user_demographics WHERE age >= 18 AND gender = 'Female' ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT source_name, last_visited FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE last_visited >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00' ORDER BY last_visited DESC;
SELECT user_name, gender, location FROM user_demographics WHERE location LIKE '%USA%' ORDER BY user_name;
SELECT source_name, traffic_count, last_visited FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY last_visited ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_sources;
SELECT source_name, visit_count FROM website_traffic_sources ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, location FROM user_demographics WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT report_date, unique_visitors, pageviews FROM report_data WHERE unique_visitors > 1000;
SELECT r.report_id, w.source_name, u.user_name FROM report_data r, website_traffic_sources w, user_demographics u WHERE r.source_id = w.source_id AND r.user_id = u.user_id ORDER BY r.report_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_sources ORDER BY source_name DESC;
SELECT source_name, visit_count, source_id FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE visit_count > 100;
SELECT user_name, age, location FROM user_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY user_name;

SELECT r.report_id, w.source_name, u.user_name, r.report_date FROM report_data r JOIN website_traffic_sources w ON r.source_id = w.source_id JOIN user_demographics u ON r.user_id = u.user_id WHERE r.unique_visitors > 1000;

SELECT w.source_name, u.user_name, r.unique_visitors, r.pageviews FROM report_data r JOIN website_traffic_sources w ON r.source_id = w.source_id JOIN user_demographics u ON r.user_id = u.user_id WHERE r.pageviews > 500 ORDER BY r.pageviews DESC;
SELECT user_name, user_age FROM user_demographics;
SELECT * FROM user_traffic_data WHERE pages_visited > 10 ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT user_name, action_type, action_date FROM user_actions WHERE action_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY action_date ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_gender FROM user_demographics;
SELECT u.user_name, w.traffic_source_name FROM user_demographics u JOIN website_traffic_sources w ON u.user_id = w.traffic_source_id;
SELECT * FROM user_demographics;
SELECT user_name, user_age, user_gender FROM user_demographics WHERE user_age > 30 ORDER BY user_age DESC;

SELECT u.user_name, w.traffic_source_name, utd.visit_date FROM user_demographics u JOIN user_traffic_data utd ON u.user_id = utd.user_id JOIN website_traffic_sources w ON utd.traffic_source_id = w.traffic_source_id WHERE utd.pages_visited > 10 ORDER BY u.user_name, utd.visit_date;
SELECT u.user_name, ua.action_type, ua.action_date FROM user_demographics u JOIN user_actions ua ON u.user_id = ua.user_id WHERE ua.action_type = 'click' AND u.user_gender = 'Male';

SELECT user_name, SUM(pages_visited) AS total_pages_visited FROM user_demographics u JOIN user_traffic_data utd ON u.user_id = utd.user_id GROUP BY user_name HAVING total_pages_visited > 50 ORDER BY total_pages_visited DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_sources ORDER BY traffic_count DESC;
SELECT source_name, traffic_count FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count > 1000;
SELECT username, age, gender FROM user_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 25 AND 35;
SELECT source_name, referral_count FROM referral_sources WHERE referral_count < 500 ORDER BY referral_count ASC;
SELECT user_id, start_time FROM user_sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT id, source_name, traffic_count FROM website_traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count > 100 ORDER BY traffic_count DESC;
SELECT user_id, username, age, gender FROM user_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 25 AND 35 ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT page_id, user_id, timestamp FROM page_views WHERE page_id = 5 AND user_id = 10 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT source_id, source_name, referral_count FROM referral_sources WHERE referral_count > 50 ORDER BY referral_count ASC;
